{"tid":892702,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"勁洗腦！「皇帝」黎明喪鬧人廢柴","createTime":"2018-11-07T05:31:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-07T06:12:56.000Z","uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"8fe1a814cac0761f1052456c7be5b6e2ed8b3fef","tid":892702,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T05:31:19.000Z","msg":"內地網劇《將夜》最近正在熱播，更邀請到天王黎明（Leon）、鄭少秋、胡軍等大卡士演員客串演出，而男主角則由一位18歲嘅男新人主演，佢係導演陳凱歌個仔！ <br />\n<br />\n雖然Leon戲份唔多，但討論度最高嘅，竟然係Leon於劇入面嘅對白。Leon飾演唐王李仲易，佢不時都用「廢柴」一詞嚟鬧一眾大臣，好多網民都質疑古裝戲竟然會有「廢柴」咁新潮嘅用詞，亦有部分網民話畀佢呢句「廢柴」洗咗腦，每集嘅樂趣變成數吓佢一共講咗幾多次「廢柴」。 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20181106/mobile/bkn-20181106190225444-1106_00862_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20181106%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20181106190225444-1106_00862_001.html&d=8pkJm4AEPJNnEtdN9MQM%2BUbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=af97332c\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20181106/mobile/bkn-20181106190225444-1106_00862_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"aecb11a2a76b554dc22ee516d7de6e48a2185d12","tid":892702,"uid":42820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T06:09:47.000Z","msg":"我說在座各位都是廢柴"},{"pid":"cf198c5800d7549047d8e6780f3f037e4432204f","tid":892702,"uid":8636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aecb11a2a76b554dc22ee516d7de6e48a2185d12","tid":892702,"uid":42820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T06:09:47.000Z","msg":"我說在座各位都是廢柴"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T06:12:56.000Z","msg":"應該講番佢當年句對白<br />\n話D大臣係垃圾"}]}